Enum Class PlayerKits

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<PlayerKits>
PlayerKits
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PlayerKits>, Constable
public enum PlayerKits extends Enum<PlayerKits>
Represents the player kits in the game. Each player kit has a name, a token icon, and a token stack.
